        <show_scrollbar>false</show_scrollbar>
        <text>Each controllable component on a mimic will have a ‘faceplate’ to provide information about the component and options to control it and adjustable process variables.

- Faceplate sizes shall be fixed and not adjustable by the user - 575 x 943.

- Each component faceplate shall open within the mimic at a fixed position.

- User shall not be able to move faceplates within mimics and windows.

- Only one faceplate shall be on display at any given time.

- A component’s faceplate shall only appear when a user clicks on a component. When no component is selected a default legend faceplate is displayed.


The control pane is provided in standard in ../templates/ControlPane.opi. This pane manages by default a legend  and display a faceplate according to the user selection.</text>
